ABOUT ELITE
ELITE PHARMACEUTICALS
is a specialty pharmaceutical company specializing in niche generics and committed to the development of abuse-deterrent opioids to help curb diversion, misuse and abuse.
Read More


ABUSE-DETERRENT TECHNOLOGY
Elite has a pipeline of opioid abuse-deterrent products under development utilizing the company’s proprietary pharmacological abuse-deterrent technology. This platform technology works with all opioids.
See How Our Technology Works


