Elite Pharmaceuticals Inc.


            
            Elite Pharmaceuticals, Inc. is a pharmaceutical company, which specializes in the development and manufacture of oral, controlled-release products, using proprietary know-how and technology, as it relates to abuse resistant products. Its strategy includes off-patent drug products for life cycle management and developing generic versions of controlled-release drug products. The company was founded on October 1, 1997 and is headquartered in Northvale, NJ.

            
            (See Full Profile)


  



 


